PASTEURIZED PROCESS AMERICAN CHEESE: CHEDDAR CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES), WATER, SODIUM CITRATE, MILKFAT, SALT, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SORBIC ACID (PRESERVATIVE), APO-CAROTENAL (COLOR), SOY LECITHIN (NON-STICKING AGENT). FULLY COOKED BACON (SMOKE FLAVORING ADDED): BACON CURED WITH: WATER, SUGAR, SALT, SMOKE FLAVORING, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, SODIUM ERYTHORBATE, SODIUM NITRITE.
